nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE HEADING NORTH-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EASTERN PACIFIC...
summary: ...OCTAVE HEADING NORTH-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EASTERN PACIFIC... As of 8:00 PM MST Tue Sep 30 the center of Octave was located near 10.8, -114.4 with movement NNW at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
